* Dinobot snarled, so the rat was not a Predacon? That fact surprise him. He 
never truly hatted Rattrap, they had had an understanding and that was all 
they needed.But now he at least had a reason to call him down and slag him.
He smiled to himself as he remembered the last words that Rattrap had said 
to him before he had departed towards the Matrix, he would have never 
guessed that he would join the Predacons.
He wasn't surprised that SilverBolt was still with the Maximals, his loyalty 
was without question.
But what happened with the others still was a mystery to him, and obviously 
to Tavatron as well.
He thought of the question that Tavatron was now going to ask him and 
wondered if he could answer it, he would if he could.*

" Yes."
